{"tid":1370197,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何重建警隊？如何撥亂反正？第一步：","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T08:38:26.000Z","uid":137220,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58f1d2625fe2010a7e2660ce48818a8cac0d90a4","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"道完歉，下一步就係補救吧<br />\n請各位放下仇恨，因為一個始終社會需要正義，中立，專業ge警察。<br />\n<br />\n先講結論：<br />\n高層要換血，重塑專業警隊文化；但大部份前線要放過<br />\n<br />\n請睇曬先負評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查委員會就一撚定</span><br />\n<br />\n但第一步係<span style=\"color: red;\">向高層開刀</span>，果d咩處長，元朗副處長，指揮官一定要先紀律處分/解僱，甚至檢控。政務司司長/特首亦要收皮，但依家集中講警察。<br />\n<br />\n係話比班前線同低層知，我連你老細都陏得，更加可以陏埋你。即刻聽話曬。<br />\n<br />\n再者，陏高層阻力係非常細：<br />\n對於其他同樣高層ge, 係減少左競爭對手<br />\n<br />\n對於D中層，依家空左幾個高層位，直頭係上位機會，恨不得你立即收皮。當然，最終上位ge一定要係政治中立，無任何與民為敵紀錄<br />\n<br />\n對於低層，WFC? 關我撚事？<br />\n<br />\n所以係內部黎講，甚至可能係支持&gt;反對<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但對於低層前線</span>，我建議只針對部份明顯違規人員，捉番打得最狼果幾個仆街出黎殺雞警猴。但對於大部份其他低層，<span style=\"color: red;\">採用類似以前港英肅貪ge手法，唔去追究</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但呢樣嘢一定要同不檢控義士捆綁</span><br />\n<br />\n點解要放過呢班人？因為佢地人數最多，阻力最大，而佢地的確係棋子，好大程度係睇上面頭。重建係靠高層，隨著時間，黑警會自然流失。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯，係妥協，但最可行最有效。"},{"pid":"922409e63901483ee6966ac8ec9a2366ac42a3be","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e1ade6cc6ee24a0237a330ec720396963efbcb","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9e9e12f739ba978b627b2e462c3a7fa013c25e","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會捉番d仆街出黎問責，跟著呢？<br />\n警隊會因為咁變好？<br />\n<br />\n定係我地真係可以炒曬呢班人？<br />\n<br />\n求教"},{"pid":"aacd97caba9d790281b5f231226fa8c1324bb482","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"由14年到依家，警察都係人民ge對立面<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以改變到？"},{"pid":"573b0da777c00a951735a202daa5ccbcc1dd0467","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:37:13.000Z","msg":"簡單講，獨立調查委員會係第一步，但唔足夠<br />\n<br />\n因為警隊都仲係果隊警隊，真正訴求應該係 <span style=\"color: red;\">重建警隊</span>"},{"pid":"f6ba2cee2d9c0bf488f099eff39d7ea069d859f2","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b6f88c85b22c6cd291da134f076e9987268797","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3d5fcb33c0e807725816a752b96d9eb0b58bee","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9942db6062d759bfbd87bc370a8d40d385f1a98","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e76bfbcdb136e574eafcc53b7d2a37699d53e5","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548780980737de68f33cc825b2a9f67287f000d5","tid":1370197,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f99e15e2f7a4e9f6b5437d672f5493def00d715","tid":1370197,"uid":5995,"like":0,"di